          "source": "专题二  简单直流电路",
          "year": 2025,
          "difficulty": 0.65,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有一个电流表，内阻为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">100Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，满偏电流为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3mA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，要把它改装成量程为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">6V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电压表，需要</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"1\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的分压电阻；若要把它改装成量程为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电流表，则需</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"2\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的分流电阻。</span></p></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\">① <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1900</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;② <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.1</span></span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"\"><span>改装成电压表<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>根据串联电路分压原理，串联电阻R分担的电压U</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span> = U - U</span><sub><span>g</span></sub><span>，其中U = 6V是改装后电压表的量程，Ug = IgRg是电流表满偏时的电压，Ig = 3mA = 0.003A，Rg = 100Ω，则Ug = 0.003A×100Ω=0.3V，所以U</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span> = 6V - 0.3V = 5.7V。 </span></p><p style=\"\"><span>由Ig=U</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span>/R可得，R=5.7/0.003=1900Ω。<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"\"><span>改装成电流表<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>根据并联电路分流原理，I = I</span><sub><span>g</span></sub><span> +I</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span>，I = 3A是改装后电流表的量程，I</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span>=Ug/R，Ug = 0.3V，I</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span> = I - I</span><sub><span>g</span></sub><span> = 3A - 0.003A = 2.997A</span></p><p style=\"\"><span>R=U</span><sub><span>g</span></sub><span>/I</span><sub><span>R</span></sub><span>=0.3/2.997=0.1Ω。<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"\"><span>故答案依次为：1900；0.1。</span></p></div></div>",
