          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">某电阻两端加</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电压时，通过的电流为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则该电阻的阻值为</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"1\" size=\"5\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；当电压改为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">6V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时，该电阻的阻值为</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"2\" size=\"5\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\">① <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3Ω</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;② <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3Ω</span></span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由欧姆定律可得</span><math latex=\"$R=\\frac{U}{I}=\\frac{3\\mathrm{V}}{1\\mathrm{A}}=3\\Upomega$\"><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>U</mi><mi>I</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mtext>V</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mtext>A</mtext></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。电阻是导体本身的一种性质，其大小只与它本身的物理条件（长度、横截面积、材料的性质、温度）有关，当电压改为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">6V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时，该电阻的阻值不变，仍为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div></div>",
